---
/**
 * Thank you page — shown after email confirmation.
 * Worker redirects here after successful /confirm.
 */
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+3:wght@400;600;700&family=Source+Serif+4:opsz,wght@8..60,400;8..60,700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Inscrição confirmada | Hipsters Builders</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="page">
      <div class="brand">
        <span class="brand-h">Hipsters</span><span class="brand-dot">.</span><span class="brand-b">builders</span>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Confirmado</p>
        <h1 class="title">Você está dentro!</h1>
        <p class="text">
          Sua inscrição foi confirmada. A próxima edição da newsletter
          chega direto no seu e-mail.
        </p>
        <p class="text">
          Enquanto isso, acompanhe a comunidade e convide quem também está buildando.
        </p>
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}`} class="link">Voltar ao site</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

<style is:inline>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    background: #f5f1e8;
    color: #1e1e1a;
    font-family: 'Source Sans 3', system-ui, sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .page { max-width: 28rem; }
  .brand { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .brand-h { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1e1e1a; }
  .brand-dot { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #c4342d; }
  .brand-b { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; color: #35342f; }
  .card { background: #fefbf4; border-top: 3px solid #c56e4a; padding: 2.5rem 2rem; }
  .eyebrow { font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #c56e4a; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .title { font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: #1e1e1a; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.2; }
  .text { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.65; color: #35342f; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .link { display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: #c56e4a; text-decoration: none; }
  .link:hover { color: #a95636; }
</style>
